speak.skill_code:
def speak(text: str):
    """
    The robot speaks the given text.

    Parameters:
    - text: The text to be spoken by the robot.
    """

    pcm_data, sample_rate = tts_processor.text_to_speech(text)
    audio_manager.get_speaker().play_audio(pcm_data, sample_rate)

    return True
